cdata.name: Dnotes
cdata.desc:
First launched in February 2014, DNotes is a blockchain-based digital currency and payment system developed by DNotes Global Inc. It allows users to perform crypto transactions within the platform. In addition, DNotes features a vault service named DNotes Vault as well as a news and information media outlet, the DCEBrief.

The NOTE token is a Scrypt-based algorithm cryptocurrency. It is open source, uses a Proof of Stake (PoS) mechanism to reward, and charge a 0.005 NOTE fee for each transaction made with the token.
